07:54.882 --> 07:58.247
in the temples, the place where you're supposed to go and worship.

07:58.628 --> 08:01.191
The temples, they had temple prostitution.

08:01.712 --> 08:05.758
And it's hard to imagine what they would have orgies and they had idol worship.

08:05.818 --> 08:07.821
Instead of worshiping God, they'd worship these idols.

08:08.282 --> 08:11.927
And it's even hard to say out loud, but they would have child sacrifices.

08:12.508 --> 08:20.740
And so parents would literally sacrifice children to the false God molek, hoping that this false God would somehow give them favor.

08:21.221 --> 08:24.786
And all these people in this horrible tense time,

08:24.898 --> 08:30.486
They were terrified at a potential attack from their enemies, the Babylonians.

