09:03.467 --> 09:15.680
And he complained to God and asked God in Habakkuk 1-2, he said this, he said, how long, Lord, must I call for help, but you do not listen.

09:15.740 --> 09:17.682
God, I'm praying, I'm begging you, but

09:17.826 --> 09:19.248
