09:39.874 --> 09:45.842
He's going, God, I'm trying to trust you, but what I see, it's hard to reconcile with who I thought you were.

09:46.562 --> 09:49.807
And what I like about Habakkuk is the dude is just honest.

09:50.808 --> 09:52.591
I mean, he's not being dramatic.

09:53.432 --> 09:56.096
He's just pouring out his hearse to God.

09:56.116 --> 09:57.858
I mean, his world has fallen apart.

09:58.439 --> 10:00.262
And he's saying, God, you don't seem to care.

10:00.302 --> 10:02.665
And that's not who I thought you were.

10:02.685 --> 10:04.568
