10:29.384 --> 10:41.362
And it blesses me because it shows me, like right here in God's word, that faith and frustration can coexist at the same time.

10:42.146 --> 10:46.893
In other words, you can not understand God or even doubt God is still believing God.

10:47.774 --> 10:55.384
And I know what I'm saying is gonna make some people mad because there's some Christians that think like when you ask questions, that's just demonstrating a lack of faith in God.

10:56.065 --> 11:01.573
